WEBVTT

00:00:35.320 --> 00:00:45.400
Support Admin Watch on
kissasia.cam or kisskh.org

00:01:09.079 --> 00:01:10.599
Why did you come without saying a word?

00:01:12.400 --> 00:01:13.719
The long journey here...

00:01:13.719 --> 00:01:14.799
It must have been very hard, right?

00:01:15.239 --> 00:01:16.079
Let me take a look at you.

00:01:17.400 --> 00:01:18.760
I'm not tired.

00:01:18.840 --> 00:01:20.640
It's you...

00:01:20.640 --> 00:01:21.760
You've gotten darker.

00:01:21.760 --> 00:01:23.079
And thinner.

00:01:24.079 --> 00:01:25.040
During this time,

00:01:25.040 --> 00:01:26.799
your work must have been very hard.

00:01:28.599 --> 00:01:30.120
Silly Meiduo.

00:01:30.120 --> 00:01:31.519
This...

00:01:31.519 --> 00:01:33.959
is strength.

00:01:34.760 --> 00:01:35.760
Recently, the work

00:01:35.760 --> 00:01:36.959
has had some setbacks.

00:01:37.640 --> 00:01:38.799
But for our fellow Tibetans

00:01:38.799 --> 00:01:40.840
to live a life of equality and freedom,

00:01:41.359 --> 00:01:42.400
a little hardship

00:01:42.400 --> 00:01:43.200
is nothing.

00:01:44.680 --> 00:01:46.239
I often think of

00:01:46.239 --> 00:01:47.879
what you said when you left.

00:01:49.560 --> 00:01:51.840
"I want to build our hometown with you."

00:01:52.680 --> 00:01:54.599
I study hard every day.

00:01:55.280 --> 00:01:56.480
I want to grow up quickly,

00:01:57.159 --> 00:01:58.400
return to Xizang quickly,

00:01:59.640 --> 00:02:00.640
and I also want

00:02:02.079 --> 00:02:03.200
to see you soon.

00:02:05.599 --> 00:02:06.760
I know.

00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:17.159
These letters...

00:02:17.159 --> 00:02:18.240
I

00:02:18.240 --> 00:02:20.199
treasure them like precious gems.

00:02:20.759 --> 00:02:22.240
I read them over and over every day.

00:02:22.840 --> 00:02:26.439
They are like charcoal fire in the cold winter,

00:02:27.360 --> 00:02:28.439
always warming me.

00:02:32.879 --> 00:02:34.560
Let me show you to your dormitory.

00:02:34.840 --> 00:02:36.080
There's no hurry yet.

00:02:36.599 --> 00:02:38.639
I have something more important to tell you.

00:02:41.240 --> 00:02:43.000
This is a handwritten letter from Balu Yundan.

00:02:43.240 --> 00:02:45.240
I must deliver it to Lord Balu myself.

00:02:47.879 --> 00:02:49.960
Balu Dunzhu is a figure

00:02:49.960 --> 00:02:51.639
of great influence locally.

00:02:54.960 --> 00:02:55.719
Tomorrow,

00:02:55.719 --> 00:02:57.639
I can accompany you to visit him

00:02:57.840 --> 00:02:58.879
in my capacity as Director of the Reform Office.

00:02:59.479 --> 00:03:00.319
We must try to get him

00:03:00.319 --> 00:03:01.879
to stand with the people and the Preparatory Committee.

00:03:03.039 --> 00:03:05.439
This is also very important work.

00:03:06.159 --> 00:03:06.960
Mm-hmm.

00:03:07.879 --> 00:03:09.400
But right now,

00:03:09.400 --> 00:03:11.560
there's an even more important task.

00:03:11.960 --> 00:03:13.400
What more important task?

00:03:15.199 --> 00:03:17.360
You get some proper rest first.

00:03:25.080 --> 00:03:26.120
Deji!

00:03:40.680 --> 00:03:41.479
Meiduo!

00:03:43.560 --> 00:03:45.159
I just had a nightmare.

00:03:47.159 --> 00:03:50.039
I dreamed my sister and I escaped from Balu Manor,

00:03:51.159 --> 00:03:52.439
only to be caught and dragged back.

00:03:59.439 --> 00:04:00.240
Don't be afraid.

00:04:00.800 --> 00:04:03.360
You are now Captain Gesang of the work team.

00:04:03.800 --> 00:04:04.840
No one dares to arrest you.

00:04:06.360 --> 00:04:07.560
Besides,

00:04:07.560 --> 00:04:09.240
I'm here with you.

00:04:19.079 --> 00:04:20.439
Thank you, Brother Gao Yuan.

00:04:21.439 --> 00:04:22.800
If I hadn't met you,

00:04:25.800 --> 00:04:27.759
everything in my dream just now

00:04:30.000 --> 00:04:31.759
would have been my sister's and my fate.

00:04:34.680 --> 00:04:36.480
You mustn't think that way.

00:04:37.240 --> 00:04:38.279
Tomorrow, when you deliver the letter,

00:04:38.959 --> 00:04:40.079
I'll be right by your side.

00:04:41.480 --> 00:04:42.439
Mm-hmm.

00:05:14.480 --> 00:05:15.360
We were born...

00:05:15.360 --> 00:05:18.399
The Balu name is branded in our bones.

00:05:19.000 --> 00:05:20.040
We can't escape it.

00:05:20.040 --> 00:05:21.639
We can't escape it.

00:05:49.240 --> 00:05:51.040
Lord! Lord!

00:05:51.879 --> 00:05:52.480
Lord!

00:05:52.480 --> 00:05:53.600
Disaster has come!

00:05:53.839 --> 00:05:55.439
The runaway Meiduo has returned!

00:05:55.680 --> 00:05:56.800
She's brought the Liberation Army

00:05:56.800 --> 00:05:58.879
to take revenge and settle scores with us!

00:05:59.040 --> 00:05:59.680
Lord,

00:05:59.680 --> 00:06:00.839
let's flee quickly!

00:06:04.120 --> 00:06:05.279
Guests...

00:06:05.279 --> 00:06:06.839
Since the door curtain has been lifted,

00:06:07.160 --> 00:06:09.439
the butter tea must be brought to a boil.

00:06:09.439 --> 00:06:10.079
Go.

00:06:10.759 --> 00:06:11.839
Invite them in.

00:06:18.560 --> 00:06:19.879
I was wondering why today

00:06:19.879 --> 00:06:22.199
the magpies on the roof were chattering so.

00:06:22.439 --> 00:06:24.279
So it's because distinguished guests have arrived!

00:06:24.759 --> 00:06:27.040
Director Li graces us with your presence.

00:06:27.439 --> 00:06:28.199
Come,

00:06:28.199 --> 00:06:28.720
please sit.

00:06:29.560 --> 00:06:30.439
Wangjiu,

00:06:30.759 --> 00:06:32.600
serve tea to our honored guests.

00:06:49.680 --> 00:06:51.240
I'll do it myself.

00:06:51.240 --> 00:06:52.959
The Liberation Army believes in equality for all.

00:06:58.839 --> 00:07:00.079
Greetings, Lord Balu.

00:07:00.839 --> 00:07:02.079
We visit unannounced today

00:07:02.439 --> 00:07:05.160
representing the Shannan Prefectural Party Committee and Naidong County Party Committee.

00:07:05.360 --> 00:07:06.399
We are also accompanied by

00:07:06.680 --> 00:07:08.040
Captain Gesang Meiduo,

00:07:08.199 --> 00:07:10.680
who will soon lead democratic reform work at Balu Manor.

00:07:12.000 --> 00:07:13.199
We have come to meet and talk with you.

00:07:18.759 --> 00:07:21.560
We wish to discuss with you in detail,

00:07:22.240 --> 00:07:23.600
based on the latest policies of the Xizang Preparatory Committee,

00:07:23.680 --> 00:07:24.319
regarding

00:07:24.319 --> 00:07:25.399
the disposition of the manor's land

00:07:26.079 --> 00:07:27.959
and means of production.

00:07:28.680 --> 00:07:29.600
We hope you

00:07:29.600 --> 00:07:30.839
can fully understand

00:07:31.040 --> 00:07:32.480
and cooperate in implementing these policies.

00:07:33.639 --> 00:07:34.720
Yundan

00:07:34.720 --> 00:07:36.800
wrote to me half a year ago about this.

00:07:38.160 --> 00:07:39.079
Ah,

00:07:41.439 --> 00:07:42.399
I

00:07:42.399 --> 00:07:44.240
support the reforms.

00:07:44.360 --> 00:07:45.199
Here are the title deeds.

00:07:46.000 --> 00:07:47.839
The livestock goes to the commune,

00:07:48.199 --> 00:07:50.000
the land is returned to the serfs.

00:07:51.800 --> 00:07:52.800
Meiduo,

00:07:52.839 --> 00:07:53.839
all these years,

00:07:53.839 --> 00:07:55.879
it's not just you who have been learning and progressing.

00:07:56.079 --> 00:07:58.439
We old folks who stayed in Xizang

00:07:58.759 --> 00:08:00.000
have also been learning

00:08:00.360 --> 00:08:01.439
and progressing!

00:08:01.439 --> 00:08:03.800
Ah ha ha ha ha!

00:08:03.800 --> 00:08:04.600
Lord Balu,

00:08:04.759 --> 00:08:06.560
your understanding and support for the reforms

00:08:06.560 --> 00:08:07.800
is a wise decision.

00:08:08.560 --> 00:08:09.759
The Preparatory Committee

00:08:09.759 --> 00:08:11.079
keeps its word.

00:08:11.560 --> 00:08:12.839
As long as you abide by the policies

00:08:13.079 --> 00:08:13.879
and cooperate with the work,

00:08:14.240 --> 00:08:14.800
the Preparatory Committee

00:08:14.800 --> 00:08:16.959
will guarantee all your and your family's legitimate rights.

00:08:19.040 --> 00:08:20.160
Yundan

00:08:20.160 --> 00:08:21.639
is progressing rapidly at the public school.

00:08:21.959 --> 00:08:22.839
Both he and Deji

00:08:24.879 --> 00:08:25.839
are good comrades.

00:08:27.639 --> 00:08:28.560
Lord Balu,

00:08:28.959 --> 00:08:30.959
when I returned from the Tibetan Public School,

00:08:31.600 --> 00:08:33.279
your son, Balu Yundan,

00:08:33.279 --> 00:08:35.799
asked me to bring you a letter.

00:08:45.440 --> 00:08:46.279
Father

00:08:47.440 --> 00:08:48.559
Only after leaving this plateau

00:08:49.080 --> 00:08:50.840
did I realize how vast the world is.

00:08:52.279 --> 00:08:54.879
Our homeland is too backward.

00:08:54.879 --> 00:08:57.240
Our fellow villagers suffer too much.

00:08:58.679 --> 00:09:00.360
For the first time, I understood

00:09:01.159 --> 00:09:02.399
that all people are born

00:09:02.399 --> 00:09:05.799
with bones equally white.

00:09:05.799 --> 00:09:07.960
We sweat together,

00:09:07.960 --> 00:09:10.240
and share the same joy of harvest.

00:09:14.799 --> 00:09:15.679
Finally,

00:09:15.679 --> 00:09:17.240
I must confess to you.

00:09:18.639 --> 00:09:20.639
I have truly fallen in love with Gesang Deji.

00:09:22.759 --> 00:09:25.120
I absolutely forbid him to be with Gesang Deji!

00:09:25.639 --> 00:09:27.279
Back then,

00:09:27.279 --> 00:09:29.000
I sent him to study on the mainland

00:09:29.159 --> 00:09:30.440
to broaden his horizons,

00:09:30.440 --> 00:09:31.399
to gain knowledge.

00:09:32.600 --> 00:09:33.799
Who could have imagined

00:09:34.639 --> 00:09:36.240
he would stoop so low?

00:09:36.240 --> 00:09:38.919
To abandon his own father

00:09:38.919 --> 00:09:40.360
for a lowly

00:09:40.399 --> 00:09:41.919
hereditary serf woman!